GenomicsDBImport.sh：merging gVCFs into GenimicsDB

GenotypeGVCFs.sh：joint genotyping

HaplotypeCaller.sh：calculating variant calls

mapping.sh：filtering out low-quality reads and mapping

population_variation_summary.sh：filtering SNPs and summarizing the VCF dataset

reference_index.sh：preparing reference and index

hybrid_founding_bees_structure.sh：calculating genetic ancestry of hybrid and founding bees

purebred_honeybee_structure.sh：calculating genetic ancestry of purebred bees

tree.R：called by purebred_honeybee_structure.sh and estimating a neighbor-joining tree.